longBusinessSummary: El Nino Ventures Inc., an exploration stage company, acquires, explores, and develops mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for zinc, lead, copper, silver, and gold deposits. It holds a 31.48% interest in the Murray Brook Project located to the west of Bathurst, New Brunswick. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
